text: Kashkarovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kashkarovsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 416 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Zilair. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Kashkarovo
